parameters:
Queen Caron: The black pearl of the empire... The pearl,
which is the symbol of me, will become more valuable than
gold.
Queen Caron: It is necessary for the future funding.

Queen Caron: You maids, disappear! Go back to your
appropriate duties.

Maid Amina: Please forgive my rudeness, Queen Caron-sama. I
would like to express my gratitude for the care I received
from you and Mother Dalsa, even if it's just a few words.

Queen Caron: Oh, you're Amina! You've grown quite
beautiful.

Queen Caron: As promised, it seems you have taken care of
Luid. As a token of my gratitude, is there anything I can do
for you?

Maid Amina: Could I have the opportunity to work under Lord
Luid? I have proper maid etiquette and also possess skills
in guarding.

Queen Caron: That's reliable of you, but you don't seem to
have any desire for a job.

Maid Amina: Queen Caron-sama, what I desire is [all of the
work].

Queen Caron: I thought you were clever since you were
young... Hahaha, very well, you may be involved in [all of
the work].

Queen Caron: Just like before, I will continue to rely on
my son from now on.

When I was called Amina, I felt an indescribable sense of
discomfort. Caron, who remained beautiful as if time had
stopped. However, the Caron I knew was completely different.

Amina will come to know the tasks that should be carried out
by the Imperial Dark Division, Ishekel. While controlling
the boundless Luid for the sake of Caron, she will protect
Luid in the world of darkness.

In those days, I was always waiting for an opportunity. A
situation and presence that would break the chains of Luid.

And so, perhaps the first and last opportunity arrived. She
staked everything on the Adventurer's Guild to save Luid.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
